data.description: Welcome to this updated beachside beauty on sought after John Anderson. Sitting on a large corner lot across from the Halifax River. The kitchen is a chef's DREAM! Boasting solid wood white shaker cabinets, Cambria quartz counter tops, stainless steel WOLF stove top and oven, tile back splash, and pendant lighting. A huge island with extra storage that overlooks the dining room with peak-a-boo views of the Intracoastal. An open concept living area, brick wood burning fireplace, LVP flooring, 5 1/4 -inch base boards, and LED dimmable lighting throughout. Generously sized bedrooms + closet space. Additionally, this home offers a BONUS room with wet bar, 3 covered patios (one is screened), fenced in back yard, and oversized 2-car garage. Probate has been finalized. All information taken from the tax record, and while deemed reliable, cannot be guaranteed.
